# @name searchByServiceArea
POST {{basePath}}/search/servicearea
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queryText":"GALLI",
  "brand":"141",
  "region":19,
  "province":"MI",
  "fuelType":"1-x",
  "priceOrder":"asc"
}

